            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Win rate, loss rate, and net P&L</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Strategy changes and the data behind each decision</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Failed experiments and why they were killed</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] shrink-0">+</span>
              <p>Risk parameters and position sizing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What we don't promise -->
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-red] text-sm mb-4">WHAT WE DON'T PROMISE</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Guaranteed returns (no one can)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>"Get rich quick" with leverage</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Secret proprietary "AI" magic</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Cherry-picked backtest results</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-[--color-red] shrink-0">&times;</span>
              <p>Permanent strategies that never change</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
