          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">SCAN</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Every hour, analyze 500+ coins for statistical setups.
            Filter noise. Wait for the edge.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">EXECUTE</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Enter positions with predefined risk.
            Stop-loss and take-profit set before entry. No exceptions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] text-center">
          <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-4xl font-bold mb-2">PROVE</p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Every result published to Telegram in real-time.
            You see what the bot does, as it does it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">TECH STACK</h3>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-sm">
          <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[--color-border] pb-2 sm:border-0">
            <span class="text-[--color-text-muted]">Engine</span>
