          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed mb-6">
            No team. No investors. No exit strategy. Just one person building trading systems
            with AI-powered tools, testing them with real money, and publishing every result.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] leading-relaxed mb-6">
            If the bot fails, you'll see it fail. If it works, you watched it work from trade #1.
            <strong class="text-[--color-accent]">That's the deal.</strong>
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm">PRINCIPLES</h3>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Evidence over hype. Always.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Show losses. Transparency builds trust.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
              <p>Kill strategies that don't perform. No ego.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-sm">
              <span class="text-[--color-accent] font-mono shrink-0">&gt;</span>
